about_text: Telegram Bot for searching Node.js [packages](https://npmjs.com/) using API of [npms.io](https://npms.io/). Bot works with InlineMode. Open sources on [Github](https://github.com/kekdude/npms-telegram-bot/)
doc_text:
You may use search qualifiers in any combination.

`author:sindresorhus` Show or filter results by author
`maintainer:sindresorhus` Show or filter results by maintainer
`keywords:gulpplugin` Show or filter results by keywords
`not:deprecated` Exclude packages that are deprecated, unstable or insecure

For the complete list of qualifiers, please read the [Search API documentation](https://api-docs.npms.io/#api-Search-ExecuteSearchQuery)
